As a Analytics Engineer with a focus on BI, you will work on a wide range of interesting tasks to actively support the business teams in the revenue optimization process. This is a highly visible role that requires rigor, self-organization, autonomy, hands-on mentality, and entrepreneurial spirit, and will allow you to develop many transversal skills (engineering, data modeling, analytical, commercial, project and stakeholder management, amongst others).

