You possess a strong understanding of analytics engineering tools such as DBT or similar;
You have a master’s degree in Computer Science, Business Informatics, Mathematics, Industrial Engineering, or equivalent work experience;
You feel comfortable using Git;
You are fluent in English.


Nice To Have


